{"sectionId":761,"sectionIdLiteral":"761","humanId":"lesson-338","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"I am affected only by my thoughts.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 338"},"annotation":"W-338","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-338\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"761#1\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>It needs but this to let salvation come to all the world.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>For in this single thought is everyone released at last from fear.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Now has he learned that no one frightens him, and nothing can endanger him.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>He has no enemies, and he is safe from all external things.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>His thoughts can frighten him, but since these thoughts belong to him alone, he has the power to change them and exchange each fear thought for a happy thought of love.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>He crucified himself.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#1:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>Yet God has planned that His beloved Son will be redeemed.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"761#2\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Your plan is sure, my Father,‚Äîonly Yours.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>All other plans will fail.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And I will have thoughts that will frighten me, until I learn that You have given me the only Thought that leads me to salvation.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Mine alone will fail, and lead me nowhere.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"761#2:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>But the Thought You gave me promises to lead me home, because it holds Your promise to Your Son.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"It needs but this to let salvation come to all the world. For in this single thought is everyone released at last from fear. Now has he learned that no one frightens him, and nothing can endanger","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 338: I am affected only by my thoughts | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†338 ‚ÄúI am affected only by my thoughts‚Äù: It needs but this to let salvation come to all the world. For in this single‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-ego"]}},{"label":"Lesson 338","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":761,"slugs":["lesson-338","i-am-affected-only-by-my-thoughts"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"12. What Is the Ego?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":753,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-ego"]}},{"label":"Lesson 338","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":761,"slugs":["lesson-338","i-am-affected-only-by-my-thoughts"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"1